{
  "stem": "22391.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did we leave the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very badly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were leaving the ghetto, before we were leaving to go to the other ghettos, we were cleaned out by-- we had to go to a schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took all our belongings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, my case was even more difficult because the person who took my belonging was-- actually, this wasn't when we went away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From my house to go into the ghetto, it was a cousin of ours who turned Catholic short time before because they were afraid they were going to take him away, so they changed religion.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that cousin of mine is the one who pulled up my little ring that I got from my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, you can't take it with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was hurting me so much and I cried so much because it was my own cousin who we were close with-- all of a sudden, she'd become against us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whatever I had asked, she took it off from me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was hurting a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this kind of thing happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But even my mother and my little sister and brother, everybody was examined from top to toe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We shouldn't hide anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everything was taken away from us, whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this one, mine was a Jewish-- I mean, she turned non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of the time, non-Jews who did that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in that point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was our own town people who we know very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was hard because we left somehow-- somebody took us out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they closed our mouth and eyes because we were young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We shouldn't talk, because we were going into Szombathely.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
